## Middleware Mistakes

### ❌ Mistake #13: Forgetting to Call next()

```javascript
// WRONG - middleware doesn't continue
app.use((req, res, next) => {
  console.log('Request received');
  // Forgot next() - request hangs!
});
```

✅ **Solution**: Always call next()

```javascript
// CORRECT
app.use((req, res, next) => {
  console.log('Request received');
  next();
});
```

### ❌ Mistake #14: Middleware Order Issues

```javascript
// WRONG - routes before body parser
app.use('/api/users', userRoutes);
app.use(express.json());  // Too late!
```

✅ **Solution**: Correct middleware order

```javascript
// CORRECT
app.use(express.json());  // Parse body first
app.use('/api/users', userRoutes);  // Then routes
app.use(errorHandler);  // Error handler last
```

### ❌ Mistake #15: Not Handling Async Middleware

```javascript
// WRONG - async middleware without error handling
app.use(async (req, res, next) => {
  req.user = await User.findById(req.userId);
  next();
});
```

✅ **Solution**: Wrap async middleware

```javascript
// CORRECT
app.use(asyncHandler(async (req, res, next) => {
  req.user = await User.findById(req.userId);
  next();
}));
```

