## Response Format

### ❌ Mistake #21: Inconsistent Response Format

```javascript
// WRONG - different formats
res.json(user);  // Sometimes just data
res.json({ user: user });  // Sometimes wrapped
res.json({ data: user, success: true });  // Sometimes with status
```

✅ **Solution**: Use consistent format

```javascript
// CORRECT - always same format
res.json({
  success: true,
  data: user,
  message: 'User created successfully'
});
```

### ❌ Mistake #22: Wrong HTTP Status Codes

```javascript
// WRONG - 200 for everything
res.status(200).json({ error: 'User not found' });
```

✅ **Solution**: Use appropriate status codes

```javascript
// CORRECT
res.status(404).json({
  success: false,
  error: {
    code: 'NOT_FOUND',
    message: 'User not found'
  }
});

// 200 - OK
// 201 - Created
// 400 - Bad Request
// 401 - Unauthorized
// 403 - Forbidden
// 404 - Not Found
// 409 - Conflict
// 500 - Internal Server Error
```

