## Quick Reference Checklist

Before pushing code, verify:

- [ ] All async functions use try-catch or asyncHandler
- [ ] No business logic in controllers
- [ ] No direct database access in controllers
- [ ] All middleware calls next() or sends response
- [ ] Input validation applied to all routes
- [ ] Passwords are hashed
- [ ] Sensitive data excluded from responses
- [ ] Consistent response format used
- [ ] Appropriate HTTP status codes
- [ ] Pagination implemented for list endpoints
- [ ] Database queries optimized (lean, select, indexes)
- [ ] Error handling tested
- [ ] No console.log in production code

---

**Remember**: Prevention is better than debugging. Follow these patterns to avoid common pitfalls.
